br />\n18. 要物價低過香港<br />\n19. 要當地一個中國人都冇<br />\n20. 要當地香港人全部都係黃絲<br />\n21. 要做非藍領既工作, 餐廳超市果D一律唔做<br />\n22. 要上網快過香港<br />\n23. 要有亞洲餐廳係附近<br />\n24. 要至少有1000萬財產或本身有樓可賣<br />\n25. 要做太空人係香港繼續返工同時, 該國唔可以收稅, 又繼續畀戶籍你<br />\n26. 要返工唔可以辛苦過香港<br />\n<br />\n99. 要保證你出發前, 以上所有條件成立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T01:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ac0caa9fadcdeb37286a61507fb97d59701726","tid":2372502,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f138557d50c881328560a124d44d99be514975a","tid":2372502,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24f7b531e0b00a26df9ef286859578da0c1fa02","tid":2372502,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c58da196f0762641d7ed7ca0c8324d04192e0d7","tid":2372502,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T00:52:58.000Z","msg":"去Las Vegas玩囉<br />\n香港冇直飛 加拿大有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"Atlantic City is closer"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"Las Vegas is much more fun"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"I have been there three times.<br />\nThe only thing I liked was the buffet at Circus Circus. Didn't gamble."},{"pid":"e72ab21552336fa98e47fa5cf51f0eed3d413aed","tid":2372502,"uid":49685,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dc51e65c48ca72f7b6d0d60b7cb1da56ce4f9ad1","tid":2372502,"uid":22617,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T23:51:24.000Z","msg":"真 幾多人移完加拿大頂唔順返香港<br />\n天氣凍 稅又重<br />\n交通唔方便<br />\n真係唔會移加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"你移到先算啦<img src